   <head>Lirica latina - Lirica LVII</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Excita festivo populi Ferraria plausu,</l>
     <l n="2">protulit ex adytis ora verenda sacris:</l>
     <l n="3">utque sua Hippolytum prospexit templa tuentem,</l>
     <l n="4">- O claros, inquit, gens mea nacta duces!</l>
     <l n="5">Quis patre invicto gerit Hercule fortius arma?</l>
     <l n="6">Mystica quis casto castius Hippolyto?</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
